name: TMNT Higher or Lower
description:
This is a simple recreation of one of the three bonus games from Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Fall of the Foot Clan for the Game Boy. You have ten chances to guess the number, each time it will tell you to go higher or lower.

This is simply a fangame, music and sprites are from the Fall of the Foot Clan game. TMNT is owned by Nickelodeon.
